Class Jamas

java.lang.Object

cropMatrix

public static Matrix cropMatrix(Matrix T,
                                int k,
                                int j)
                         throws IllegalArgumentException
Drops the columns k+1,...,n and the rows j+1,...,m if T is a m x n-matrix.

Parameters:
T - Matrix to drop
k - columns to drop
j - rows to drop
Returns:
new j x k-matrix
Throws:
